snippet: Daniel Brooks made par on the first playoff hole Sunday to win the fog-shortened Madeira Islands Open, which was overshadowed by the death of a caddie earlier in the day.
abstract: Daniel Brooks wins Madeira Islands Open golf tournament, which is overshadowed by death of caddie Ian MacGregor earlier in the day, apparently of a heart attack.
lead_paragraph: Daniel Brooks made par on the first playoff hole Sunday to win the fog-shortened Madeira Islands Open, which was overshadowed by the death of a caddie earlier in the day.
